name: Cube Variant No.36 (Pandora's Box)
description:
Pandora was given a wedding gift of a beautiful box, with instructions to not open it under any circumstance. Impelled by her curiosity, Pandora opened the box and all evil contained therein escaped and spread over the earth.
This cube variant was created by the implementation of "Criss Cross" configuration to "X+2" subdivision on a 1x1x1 cube.
Material: Ghost
